projects. Fill missing timestamps with CURRENT_TIMESTAMP::TEXT and IsDeleted with 0. Handle empty strings as NULLs before casting to NOT NULL constraints where applicable.\nThe model transforms the installed_asset__c source table into the Installed_Asset__c target schema. Key transformations include multi-format date parsing for warranty_end_date__c (handling ISO, European DD.MM.YYYY, US MM/DD/YYYY, and YYYYMMDD formats), name normalization with INITCAP and default fallback to 'Unknown', and SAFE_NULL handling for account__c and project__c foreign keys. CreatedDate/LastModifiedDate are set to CURRENT_TIMESTAMP since the source lacks timestamps, and IsDeleted defaults to 0."
